---
title: Kidney Bean Taquitos & Charred Corn Salsa with Plant-Based Mayo
description: Taquitos, the close relative of enchiladas are in town tonight and we're excited for their stay. By switching beef to
beans, you can still get all of your favourite Mexican flavours in this delicious veggie meal! Dig in!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67592f1ab3cc8de1f221c1a1-0cc6c03a.jpeg
